PersonalMission.Name: LT-1: For Victory!
PersonalMission.Description: At lower tiers, some light tanks have almost as much firepower as heavier vehicles.
PersonalMission.Hint: Still, try to avoid face-to-face combat. Instead, try to hit enemies in the side or rear. Observe where the enemy vehicle's gun is pointing and approach from the other side.

Primary.Conditions:
•  Be among the top 3 players on your team by experience earned
•  Win
